'''Identification #43641''' was the identification given to an investor which joined the [[Dorumaa Investment Group]] sometime before the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]]. The group invested heavily in a deep-ocean landing platform, ostensibly for use as a fishing base, though no sea vessels were ever seen near it. Other investors believed #43641 to be a front for [[Thaereian military]] forces in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]].<ref name="LFC">''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

The [[Dorumaa Excavation]], a cave that held presumed proofs of native intelligent life in the Cularin system in ancient times, had been closed to any public access since before Identification #43641 was first noticed. Around [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]], Identification #43641 publicly notified that those proofs were false; however, access to the site was still forbidden.<ref name="hitc">{{LivingForce|Clouds of Genarius: Head in the Clouds}}</ref>

